{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/language/python/python_absolute","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"eb3fb19a-0705-591a-b035-cf1b8128bcad","html":"<h1 id=\"슈퍼개발자-춤추는망고입니다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%8A%88%ED%8D%BC%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EC%9E%90-%EC%B6%A4%EC%B6%94%EB%8A%94%EB%A7%9D%EA%B3%A0%EC%9E%85%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"슈퍼개발자 춤추는망고입니다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>슈퍼개발자, 춤추는망고입니다.</h1>\n<p>( <del>춤 안춥니다.</del> )</p>\n<p><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"python-에서\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#python-%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C\" aria-label=\"python 에서 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Python 에서</h2>\n<h2 id=\"절댓값을-구하고-싶다면\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%88%EB%8C%93%EA%B0%92%EC%9D%84-%EA%B5%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B3%A0-%EC%8B%B6%EB%8B%A4%EB%A9%B4\" aria-label=\"절댓값을 구하고 싶다면 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>절댓값을 구하고 싶다면!</h2>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 임의의 두 숫자의 차이를 구해요!</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">get_gap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> number2<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\"># number1과 number2의 차이!</span>\n    gap <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">abs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>number1 <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> number2<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> gap\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>get_gap<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 3 - 7 = -4 가 아닌, -4 의 절댓값 4 출력!</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"어떤-숫자가-오더라도-절댓값이-필요하다면\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%96%B4%EB%96%A4-%EC%88%AB%EC%9E%90%EA%B0%80-%EC%98%A4%EB%8D%94%EB%9D%BC%EB%8F%84-%EC%A0%88%EB%8C%93%EA%B0%92%EC%9D%B4-%ED%95%84%EC%9A%94%ED%95%98%EB%8B%A4%EB%A9%B4\" aria-label=\"어떤 숫자가 오더라도 절댓값이 필요하다면 permalink\" class=\